title: Ahmed Muhumed leads West Salem to GVC team championship
text: Ahmed Muhumed leads West Salem to GVC team championship Bill Poehler , Statesman Journal 8:21 p.m. PDT October 21, 2015 Buy Photo West Salem's Ahmed Muhumed wins the boys varsity race with a time of 15:17 during the Greater Valley Conference District Cross Country meet Wednesday, Oct. 21, 2015, at Bush's Pasture Park in Salem.
